  .body
    .container-fluid
      .row-fluid
        .span10.offset1
          .span7
            .white-box
              .testimonial
                Our members have spare office space and no way to manage it to rent out and network with other members.  It is a win win for all professionals that use our Desks Near Me marketplace.
                .avatar-row
                  .avatar-name
                    &mdash; San Jose Chamber of Commerce

            .white-box
              .testimonial
                Desks Near Me was able to help provide a new simple customizable way to list our spaces and bring it to a wider audience.  We love that they have a global reach to highlight our spaces.
                .avatar-row
                  .avatar-name
                    &mdash; Premier Business Centers

          .span5
            .white-box
              .testimonial
                With Desks Near Me, we were easily able to create whitelabel marketplace that both big businesses and freelancers could use to find professional and quiet working space with all the office type amenities they might need on the go.
                .avatar-row
                  .avatar-name
                    &mdash; San Francisco Chamber of Commerce

